# Testing

## Unit / component (Vitest)

- Co-locate tests: `foo.test.ts` next to `foo.ts`
- Use `@testing-library/react` for components; test behavior, not implementation
- Mock Supabase client at the module boundary, not fetch globally

## E2E (Playwright)

- Tests in `e2e/`; one spec per critical user journey
- Seed test org/user via Supabase test helpers or fixtures
- Critical paths: signup → create project → generate deck → export PPTX

## What to test

| Area | Priority |
|------|----------|
| Slide type validation / Zod schemas | High |
| Export layout mapping | High |
| RLS policy behavior (integration) | High |
| Auth redirect middleware | Medium |
| UI snapshot-only tests | Low |

## Rules

- No tests that hit production APIs or real Stripe/OpenAI
- Deterministic fixtures; no `Date.now()` without mocking
- Run `vitest run` and `playwright test` before merging feature work
